SELECT HOGI, MAX(CASE WHEN CHARACTERISTIC = 'ES_ASUBW' THEN VALUE1 ELSE NULL END) ES_ASUBW, MAX(CASE WHEN CHARACTERISTIC = 'ES_ARISE' THEN VALUE2 ELSE NULL END) ES_ARISE FROM ( SELECT VBAP.HOGI, CABN.ATNAM AS CHARACTERISTIC, IBSYMBOL.ATWRT AS VALUE1, IBSYMBOL.ATFLV AS VALUE2 FROM SAPHEE.VBAP VBAP INNER JOIN SAPHEE.IBIN IBIN ON VBAP.MANDT = IBIN.MANDT AND VBAP.CUOBJ = IBIN.INSTANCE INNER JOIN SAPHEE.IBINVALUES AS IBINV ON IBIN.MANDT = IBINV.MANDT AND IBIN.IN_RECNO = IBINV.IN_RECNO INNER JOIN SAPHEE.IBSYMBOL IBSYMBOL ON IBINV.MANDT = IBSYMBOL.MANDT AND IBINV.SYMBOL_ID = IBSYMBOL.SYMBOL_ID INNER JOIN SAPHEE.CABN CABN ON IBSYMBOL.MANDT = CABN.MANDT AND IBSYMBOL.ATINN = CABN.ATINN WHERE VBAP.MANDT = '183' AND VBAP.HOGI = #{POSID} AND CABN.ATNAM IN ('ES_ASUBW', 'ES_ARISE') ) T GROUP BY HOGI FOR FETCH ONLY WITH UR
